  :PROPHOTO-RGB
  :SMPTE-C-RGB
  :SRGB
  :WIDE-GAMUT-RGB

The conversion method may be passed to CONVERT via the keywords
:SPACE (for a name of a colour space) or :MATRIX for passing a
9-element vector directly.

